---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="FAQ" description="Frequently asked questions about AutoVideo mock creation.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">FAQ</span>
      <h1>Questions about AutoVideo?</h1>
      <p>Find quick answers about mock creation, exports, and collaboration.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card" style="display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
        <details open>
          <summary>Is AutoVideo a real rendering tool?</summary>
          <p>No. AutoVideo is a mock workflow designed to help you plan and align before production.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Do I need to create an account?</summary>
          <p>No login is required. You can explore mock workflows instantly.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Can I export the storyboard?</summary>
          <p>Yes. We provide script, storyboard, and timing files for your team.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>What languages do you support?</summary>
          <p>The experience is currently optimized for English prompts.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>How do I request a custom demo?</summary>
          <p>Reach out via the contact page or email admin@autovideo.videi.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
